do you just call him Michael?

00:25:42.980 --> 00:25:43.250
[? MALE SPEAKER: Michael. ?]

00:25:43.250 --> 00:25:44.650
CAROL SANFORD: It's
just easier, right?

00:25:44.650 --> 00:25:46.691
But I try to, and then I
