00:30:33.500 --> 00:30:35.150
You may know this story.

00:30:35.150 --> 00:30:38.521
When he was in Starwood,
many of the people

00:30:38.521 --> 00:30:40.020
were coming up from
the Middle East.

00:30:40.020 --> 00:30:42.160
And he also had responsibility
for the Middle East

00:30:42.160 --> 00:30:44.800
and Europe for Starwood
Resorts for food.

00:30:44.800 --> 00:30:47.090
Many of those people who
were coming up obviously

00:30:47.090 --> 00:30:50.800
did not speak the language
in the European Union

00:30:50.800 --> 00:30:52.377
very well, wherever they were.

00:30:52.377 --> 00:30:53.960
Other people thought
they were stupid.

00:30:55.000 --> 00:30:56.590
