00:30:56.590 --> 00:30:58.210
Language has nothing
to do-- you know,

00:30:58.210 --> 00:31:01.270
speaking another language has
nothing do with intelligence.

00:31:01.270 --> 00:31:02.670
Give people work to do.

00:31:02.670 --> 00:31:04.520
Find ways to put translators.

00:31:04.520 --> 00:31:10.190
And he rebuilt the entire
service system for Starwood

00:31:10.190 --> 00:31:12.364
based on using
language as a leverage

00:31:12.364 --> 00:31:14.530
and giving people the ability
to learn the language.

00:31:14.530 --> 00:31:17.960
So he actually started thinking
about that kind of global ship

00:31:17.960 --> 00:31:19.490
before he got here.

00:31:19.490 --> 00:31:22.110
He's an amazing human being,
and there's more of his stories

00:31:22.110 --> 00:31:24.690
and even of his
childhood in this book.

00:31:24.690 --> 00:31:29.300
So what I would like to do
