getting the best product.

00:31:47.260 --> 00:31:50.150
Everybody sees you out
in front as the lead.

00:31:50.150 --> 00:31:52.015
And then you have to
use that platform.

00:31:53.130 --> 00:31:54.650
And if it's a social
system, you've

00:31:54.650 --> 00:31:57.050
