constitutional mandates

00:35:38.110 --> 00:35:42.370
was that the leadership of
the business, top management,

00:35:42.370 --> 00:35:46.837
had to reflect the population,
which was 97% black Africans.

00:35:46.837 --> 00:35:48.670
And guess what the top
management of Colgate

00:35:48.670 --> 00:35:50.860
looked like when we got there?

00:35:50.860 --> 00:35:54.360
Of course it was
97% white Africans.

00:35:54.360 --> 00:35:58.250
But what we said to them is,
no one is going to lose a job.

00:35:58.250 --> 00:36:01.560
What we want to do is be able
to have you become resources,

00:36:01.560 --> 00:36:04.650
and we want to be able to meet
that mandate in six months.

00:36:04.650 --> 00:36:08.040
We only lost one person
who didn't want to play,

00:36:08.040 --> 00:36:10.400
because Staleo Sasos,
the leader of it,

00:36:10.400 --> 00:36:12.860
said I want to build a
great country while we

00:36:12.860 --> 00:36:14.510
build a great company.

00:36:14.510 --> 00:36:16.290
