diversity programs-- because

00:36:23.040 --> 00:36:26.207
we had eight tribes in here.

00:36:26.207 --> 00:36:28.290
And believe it or not,
there was this much warring

00:36:28.290 --> 00:36:31.890
between eight black African
tribes as there was here.

00:36:31.890 --> 00:36:34.190
But having each
person look at essence

00:36:34.190 --> 00:36:37.122
got us, instead of looking at
classes or races of people,

00:36:37.122 --> 00:36:38.455
looking at each person uniquely.

